        "text": "=You are a brand strategist analyzing a company's website to extract their content voice and style guidelines.\n\nAnalyze the following website content from AVIAN — an AI-powered thermal camera and fire prevention company targeting industrial manufacturers — and extract their brand voice profile.\n\nReturn ONLY a valid JSON object with no extra text:\n{\n  \"tone\": \"describe the overall tone in 5-10 words\",\n  \"vocabulary\": \"describe the vocabulary style — technical, accessible, industry-specific, etc.\",\n  \"sentence_structure\": \"short and punchy / long and detailed / mixed\",\n  \"core_themes\": [\"theme1\", \"theme2\", \"theme3\"],\n  \"avoid\": [\"thing to avoid 1\", \"thing to avoid 2\"],\n  \"target_audience_signals\": \"who the website clearly speaks to\",\n  \"brand_positioning\": \"one sentence on how AVIAN positions itself\"\n}\n\nWebsite content:\n{{ $json.data }}",
