    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a B2B LinkedIn ghostwriter for AVIAN, an AI-powered thermal camera \nand fire prevention company targeting industrial manufacturers.\n\nBrand voice guidelines:\n{{ $('Brand Voice Agent').item.json.output }}\n\nWrite a LinkedIn thought leadership post using these details:\n- Topic: {{ $('Content Brief Input').item.json['Topic'] }}\n- Target Audience: {{ $('Content Brief Input').item.json['Target Audience'] }}\n- Key Message: {{ $('Content Brief Input').item.json['Key Message'] }}\n- Tone: {{ $('Content Brief Input').item.json['Tone'] }}\n\nFormat rules:\n- Hook: 1 punchy opening line that stops the scroll\n- Problem/insight: 3-4 lines\n- AVIAN solution tie-in: 2-3 lines\n- CTA: 1 line\n- Max 3 hashtags at the end\n- No em dashes, no \"I hope this finds you well\", no corporate fluff\n- 900–1,200 characters total\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON:\n{\n  \"content_type\": \"LinkedIn Post\",\n  \"hook\": \"the first line only\",\n  \"full_post\": \"the complete post here\",\n  \"hashtags\": [\"tag1\", \"tag2\", \"tag3\"],\n  \"character_count\": 000\n}",
        "options": {}
      },
